data(iris)

colors <- c("red", "blue", "orange")
colors <- colors[(iris$Species)]

shapes <- c(15, 16, 17)
shapes <- shapes[(iris$Species)]


x <- iris$Sepal.Length
y <- iris$Petal.Length  
z <- iris$Sepal.Width

s3d <- scatterplot3d(x, y, z, col.axis = "red", col.grid = "lightblue",
              main = "Grafico 3D", pch = shapes, xlab = "Longitud del sepalo",
              ylab = "Longitud del petalo", zlab = "Anchura del sepalo",
              col.lab = "purple", type = "h", color = colors, lty.axis = "dotted")

legend("topleft", legend = levels(iris$Species),
      col = c("red", "blue", "orange"), 
      pch = c(15, 16, 17), bty = "n")

# Add regression plane
my.lm <- lm((z ~ x + y))
s3d$plane3d(my.lm, lty = "dotted")

#grafico2
x=seq(-3,3,length=100)
y=seq(-3,3,length=100)
parabola=function(x,y) x^2+y^2
z=outer(x, y, parabola)
persp(x,y,z)

ecuacionParab <- expression(z == x^2 + y^2)
persp(x,y,z,theta = 30, phi = 30,expand=0.5, col = "orange",
      main="Paraboloide", sub=ecuacionParab, col.main="blue")

#grafico3
x=seq(-10,10,length=100)
y=seq(-10,10,length=100)
parabola=function(x,y) {r<-(sqrt(x^2+y^2)); 10*sin(r)/r}
z=outer(x, y, parabola)
persp(x,y,z)

ecuacionParab <- expression(z == 10*sin(sqrt(x^2+y^2)) / sqrt(x^2+y^2))
persp(x,y,z,theta = 30, phi = 30,expand=0.5, col = rainbow(20),
      main="Paraboloide", sub=ecuacionParab, col.main="blue")

parabola=function(x,y) exp(-x^2-y^2)
z=outer(x, y, parabola)
persp(x,y,z)

ecuacionParab <- expression(z == exp(-x^2-y^2))
persp(x,y,z,theta = 30, phi = 30,expand=0.5, col = rainbow(7),
      main="Paraboloide", sub=ecuacionParab, col.main="blue")

parabola=function(x,y) {r<-sqrt(x^2+y^2); 10*sin(r)/r }
z=outer(x, y, parabola)
persp(x,y,z)

ecuacionParab <- expression(z == exp(-x^2-y^2))
persp(x,y,z,theta = 30, phi = 30,expand=0.5, col = rainbow(7),
      main="Paraboloide", sub=ecuacionParab, col.main="blue")
